~~~~~~~~~~~~~


MSN plugin
~~~~~~~~~~


Misc plugins
~~~~~~~~~~~~
[-] LiveJournal: Security level of message was set incorrectly.
[+] LiveJournal: Add optional signature to all messages.
[+] LiveJournal: Option to disable message text formatting.
[-] Proxy: fix some crashes.
